-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Desde 1995</span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 327px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>Diretriz 2005</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 131px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Comprometimento com a Excel&ecirc;ncia</span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 99px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Toda a Organização</span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 95px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Desde 2003</span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 327px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Ades&atilde;o ao PEG-EB</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Ades&atilde;o ao GESP&Uacute;BLICA</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"width: 131px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Estabelecimento de Padr&otilde;es de Trabalho</span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 99px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Toda a Organização</span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 95px; height: 27px;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Desde 1995</span></span></p></td><td style=\"width: 32